column5: Going up to the Fenelon Falls area for a week at the end of the month. Have a canoe and trolling motor ready to go and was looking for any suggestions to help catch some fish. Im a newbie fisherman and would appreciate any help...

What lake are you going to Cameron or Sturgeon? I just had a post on Cameron (should be on the second page) I found walleye and small mount in the south end (10 to 15 feet of water) and large mouth and muskie on the North West side.
